videos.description: Dartmouth arns a road win at Columbia, racking up a 76-63 decision. Aaryn Rai scored 20 to lead four players in double figures.
videos.headline: Rai scores 20 to carry Dartmouth over Columbia 76-63  - Via Ivy League
